                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9859" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0272</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">907 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从散兵游勇到集腋成裘：北控秦皇岛水务公司的一体化运营实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Fragmentation to Synergy: Integrated Operations Practice at Beijing Enterprises Qinhuangdao Water Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宋金波，辛思怡，苑贺辉，田楠林，宁彦文，陈汉涛，宋洁，高景鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北控（秦皇岛）水务有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有存量资产；一体化运营；数智赋能；运营效能；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">State-Owned Existing Asset, Integrated Operations, Digital and Intelligent Enablement, Operational Efficiency</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当前，地方政府普遍面临国有存量资产管理分散、运营效率低下的问题，如何提升国有存量资产的运营效能，已成为推动经济高质量发展的关键议题。在此背景下，北控秦皇岛水务公司与秦皇岛市展开合作，采用PPP-TOT模式，整体打包接手运营秦皇岛市总值36.8亿元的存量资产，涵盖污水处理厂、污泥处置厂、排水管网及泵站等设施，并通过厂网互联、技术升级和数智赋能，构建“厂网一体化”运营管理新模式，显著提升了整体运营效能。本案例通过对北控秦皇岛水务公司污水污泥处理项目一体化运营实践的剖析，引导学生厘清其以构建一体化运营模式为核心、引入数智技术赋能实现运营管理效能提升的独特路径，对于国有存量资产运营增效及数智化转型相关理论与实践具有借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Currently, local governments widely face the challenges of fragmented management and low operational efficiency in the operation of state-owned existing assets. Enhancing the operational performance of these assets has become a key issue in promoting high-quality economic development. Against this backdrop, Beijing Enterprises Qinhuangdao Water Company collaborated with Qinhuangdao City by adopting a PPP-TOT model, taking over the bundled operation of existing assets valued at 3.68 billion yuan. These assets include sewage treatment plants, sludge treatment plants, sewer networks, and pumping stations. Through plant-network integration, technological upgrading, and digital-intelligent empowerment, the company has built a new integrated operation and management model, significantly improving overall operational efficiency. This case study analyzes the integrated operation practices of Beijing Enterprises Qinhuangdao Water Company’s sewage and sludge treatment projects. It aims to clarify the unique aspects of the company’s core approach: establishing an integrated operation model, enabled by digital and smart technologies, to significantly improve operational and management efficiency. It provides valuable insights for the theory and practice related to enhancing the efficiency and digital transformation of state-owned existing asset operations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《项目管理》、《运营管理》、《企业数字化转型》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">委托运营模式；实现存量资产一体化运营的PPP-TOT模式；支撑一体化运营的TOE框架；一体化运营优化的DIKW模型；一体化运营绩效评价</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
